---
description: Rundler Rust workspace and tooling guardrails
globs:
  - "**/*.rs"
  - "Cargo.toml"
  - "Cargo.lock"
  - "rust-toolchain.toml"
  - ".cargo/config.toml"
  - "Makefile"
  - "deny.toml"
---

- Use Rust `1.92.0` from `rust-toolchain.toml`; use nightly only for rustfmt.
- Prefer `make fmt`, `make lint`, and `make test-unit` over ad hoc equivalents.
- Keep `tokio_unstable` from `.cargo/config.toml` in mind for builds and docs.
- Do not add `openssl` or new unknown git sources without updating `deny.toml`.
- Use `TaskSpawnerExt` for long-running library tasks instead of untracked `tokio::spawn`.

Full details: `.agents/skills/tooling/` and `.agents/skills/rust-async/`.

